============================================================
          Notes Manager v0.4.1 (01-01-2018)
============================================================
 - Image to PDF Generator:
	- Minor bug fix. Earlier, if the file 'Image_To_PDF_Generator.py' was imported into another python program,
	    it used to execute the main method in 'Image_To_PDF_Generator.py'
	- File formatted
 - .idea directory removed.
 - .gitignore updated.
