============================================================
          Notes Manager v0.3.2 (16-07-2017)
============================================================
 - Image to PDF Generator:
	- In Bookmarks, offset can be added
 	- In Bookmarks, individual page numbers can be mentioned
 	- Bug Fix: Program used to crash when the Bookmarks file or Meta-Data file or Images folder doesn't exist
 	- Bug Fix: Program used to crash when reading meta-data (if it exists)
 	- Code refined and Optimised
============================================================
============================================================


============================================================
          Notes Manager v0.3.1 (15-07-2017)
============================================================
 - Image to PDF Generator:
	- Added new optional argument - Meta-Data file with default value 'Meta-Data.txt'
 	- Title and Author will be read from Meta-Data file and hence these arguments are not required
	- Default value for argument 'Bookmarks file' set to 'Bookmarks.txt' and hence the argument is no longer mandatory
	- Added prompts for warnings whether to proceed or not
	- Code refined and Optimised
============================================================
